channel.description:
Never overestimate the power of the Summoner’s Code. The words of League of Legends players, as they appear, unedited. The proper way to view this blog is to imagine the player quotes in the voice of the champion they are representing.As the Tribunal is currently out of session, recent additions are more likely to be user experiences than actual cases until such a day as the Tribunal returns.
The Summoner’s Code continues to be made possible due to user submissions. Please click the “Summoner Submissions” button below to submit your favorite quotes.
channel.title: The Summoner's Code
